Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory170.png'}
{3: 'Not only the King, everyone was shocked and stopped to look at the light.'}
{3: 'The artifact and the Demon King merged together, turning into a blazing sphere, then transformed into a strange surface that resembled a portal.'}
{3: 'From which a familiar person walked out.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica (?)', 3: "Phew... It's been a while since I last appeared with a body.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'It really is her... Miss Celica...', 4: '1'}
{3: "The artifact answered Liv's call, and turned the Demon King into Celica."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'But will it actually help to have Celica here...', 4: '1'}
{3: "Lee was the first to respond, and his concern was actually everybody's. The artifact might be powerful, but what about Celica?"}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "If she's only a projection from Liv's M.I.N.D... There's no way that she can give us what we need.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica (?)', 3: "C'mon, you heroes... Are you questioning the power of the Goddess? I'm only using the look of Celica!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'What Goddess?', 3: '21', 4: "Aren't you the Demon King?", 5: '22'}
{2: 'Goddess', 3: 'Wait, did you just summon me, Goddess Celica, without knowing anything?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Goddess', 3: 'The Demon King is now part of me. The Goddess has no body, so I just borrowed his.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'King', 3: "It's... It's the Overlord! Ohhhhhh!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Goddess', 3: 'How many times have I told you not to call me Overlord!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'The King was the second to realize what happened. Unlike us, he immediately shouted out a name.'}
{3: 'Only to be kicked on the wall before he could even finish.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "At least we don't have to worry about her power. Whether you are Celica, or the Goddess... Could you lend your power to us?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Goddess', 3: "Of course. I answered your call, so I'm on your side, heroes.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: 'Please get rid of that King then!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Goddess', 3: 'No, heroes, you are the one to finish him off.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Why?', 3: '38', 4: "Just kick him a few more times, can't you?", 5: '39'}
{2: 'Goddess', 3: 'The Goddess is set to be the administrator of this game. I can do many things, but I can never kill any being in the game.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Goddess', 3: "Actually, I cannot do much other than delaying him... Didn't you realize the King was not damaged at all?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Um... So much efforts all wasted.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Goddess', 3: 'Not at all! Remember I said you were the one to finish him off? Right now, I, the Goddess, shall give you the latest main quest!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Celica made a "I choose you" pose, and everyone heard a strange system sound. The quest menu was automatically opened.'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Main quest updated: Defeat the evil King.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'The main quest has changed... Hey, is this a system feature...?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Camu', 3: "Correct. We couldn't kill the King because that was a system setting. But right now, our main quest is to defeat the King.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Camu', 3: 'That means he is no longer invincible. This quest can now be "completed."', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'King', 3: "...Ugh, I, I'm not going to die here!", 4: '1'}
{3: "Realizing the tide had turned, the King fled further into the Demon King's Castle. Many guards rushed out."}
{2: "Let's go!", 3: '57', 4: 'Get rid of the guards!', 5: '57'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Roger. All members, strike!', 4: '1'}
